 but if you replace your breakfast, high tea or supper with a cup of SUPEZY (only 72 kcal), the calories will greatly reduced and tt can also relieve cravings. Other than that, it can reduce the daily intake of about 500kcal and also provide required protein, vitamins and fiber. 
